gomodel:SYNGO_244  a      owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Quantitative mass spectrometric analyses (iBAQ) of purified synaptosomes indicate the presence of Rab21 in synapses.. Experimental description: From main text \"To quantify the organization of synaptic vesicle recycling, we first purified synaptic boutons (synaptosomes) from the cellular layers of the cortex and cerebellum of adult rats, using a modified version (6) of a classical brain fractionation protocol (7) (Fig. 1A).\"" ;
